	sjx input metod server

o This program supports XIMProtocol.

o This program supports 'root window' input style.

o This program needs sj3serv (Japanese conversion server).

DESCRIPTION

	In this implementation, sjx starts the Japanese conversion
with XK_Kanji. You can change other key bindings 
to modify ~/.sjrc configuration file. Please refer Sjrc file
in this directory.

